    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paper or cardboard printed with construction drawings to make 3D scale models. The construction drawing contains folding lines and adhesive edges. The model is cut or cut from the cardboard, then folded and finally glued together.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
